The paper deals with epistemic planning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also introduces a new logic, term-modal logic, which is related to modal logic (cs.LO) and first-order logic (cs.PL). The paper also discusses the use of action models and action schemas, which are relevant to multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and dynamic logic (cs.DL).
